  Secondly, profitability of freight carriers when compared 
with other firms is as follows. Route trucking has risen to the 
4-5% level and area trucking has leveled off at the 
5% level. 
On the other hand, this figure is at the fairly high level of 
7-8% for manufacturing and 7% for the retail 
industry. 
Nevertheless, in the wholesale industry this level is low at 
5%. 



  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
