|                  |                  |                  |celeration        | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


<H5>  (3) Forms of Usage in Terms of Items Conveyed </H5>
  For transport of raw materials (travel distance 200-300 km) 
and spare parts (travel distance 100-300 km), primarily 4-ton 
vehicles are used. For transport of construction materials, a 
variety of 2-ton, 4-ton and 10-ton trucks are used, and the 
operating features are diverse as well. For the transport of 
finished goods, food, daily necessities, books and printed 
material, and liquors, mainly 2-ton and 4-ton vehicles are used. 
Travel distance of around 100 km, primarily daytime trips within 
the cities, and numerous delivery items is characteristic. 



  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Chart 3-5. Forms of Usage in Terms of Items Conveyed                       | 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
